**Concurrency Handling (Edit POST):**
```csharp
catch (DbUpdateConcurrencyException ex)
{
    var entry = ex.Entries.Single();
    var clientValues = (Department)entry.Entity;
    var databaseEntry = entry.GetDatabaseValues();

    if (databaseEntry == null)
    {
        // Deleted by another user
    }
    else
    {
        var databaseValues = (Department)databaseEntry.ToObject();

        // Compare each field
        if (databaseValues.Name != clientValues.Name)
            ModelState.AddModelError("Name", $"Current value: {databaseValues.Name}");
        // ... similar for Budget, StartDate, InstructorID

        // Update RowVersion from database
        department.RowVersion = databaseValues.RowVersion;
    }
}
```

**Validation Rules:**
- Name: MinLength 3, MaxLength 50
- Budget: Decimal (no range specified)
- StartDate: DateTime (no validation)
- InstructorID: Optional (nullable)
- RowVersion: Timestamp (auto-managed by EF Core)

**Notifications Sent:**
